        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Asimov', 3: 'The greatest feature of the \"Virtual Horizon\" command system is its capability to train a commandant\\'s adaptability when forming temporary teams.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 6,
        "ActionId": 5,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'Which is why you aren\\'t provided with a fixed one. Commandants will have to draft random personnel and form a temporary team to deal with various battle scenarios.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 7,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 302,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'So I don\\'t have to command the fights themselves?', 3: '6'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 8,
        "ActionId": 6,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'This removes the unstable factors of in-battle command, and you can instead focus on team formation for Constructs.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 9,
        "ActionId": 7,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'This shouldn\\'t be a problem for you considering that you\\'ve been in numerous teams and are familiar with various types of Constructs.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 10,
        "ActionId": 8,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'And one more thing... The original system\\'s Construct database is too old. So I replaced it with the ones in our database.', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 11,
        "ActionId": 9,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Asimov', 3: 'However, this system will automatically adjust the basic performance for Constructs, so even the combat performance of support-type frames may take you by surprise.', 4: '1'}"
